                            ],
                            Label: "leave_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "I guide travelers through the deep water, and I turn back the ones who are not ready. Which are you today?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Third warden. Beat me and you are almost to the apprentice. Ready?"
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The pool does not grant wishes and it does not hoard faces. It has tadpoles in it. I keep a list of the tadpoles."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Whatever Luna and Stella told you about the water, the truth is wetter and much less dramatic. Boots off at the deep crossings. That is the whole secret."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Lyra - warden of the inner path",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
